                        extensive game library, and user-friendly interface. This award acknowledges RP Games as a go-to
                        destination for gamers seeking unparalleled gaming excellence.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-image-container">
                        <img src="./images/Web images/innovation award.png" alt="Feature 2"
                            class="img-fluid feature-image">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Innovation Leader Award</h3>
                    <p>The Innovation Leader Award highlights RP Games as a trailblazer ion the gaming industry, pushing
                        the boundaries of technology and
                        introducing innovative features that enhance the gaming experiences. This award recognizes the
                        platform's commitment to staying ahead of the curve and continuously striving for
                        groundbreaking advancements.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-image-container">
                        <img src="./images/Web images/community.png" alt="Feature 3" class="img-fluid feature-image">
                    </div>
